{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふふ、はい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hehe, yes.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "キャロリのまとめてくれたリストを見ながら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "While looking at the list that Karori had compiled,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "プリマは照れ隠しに次の調合を聞いていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Prima asked about the next concoction to hide her embarrassment."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、それにはこの薬草も入れるといいよ〜」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, you should also add this herb to it~\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「へ？　そうなの？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh? Really?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「へー、全然知りませんでした」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Wow, I had no idea at all.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うん、精力が増してねぇ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, it increases vitality,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　心臓の動悸が速くなって、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the heartbeat speeds up,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　軽い興奮状態になって……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and you get into a light state of excitement...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「もう媚薬として使うと効果抜群！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It’s super effective as an aphrodisiac!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「媚薬を作る気はないよ！？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I have no intention of making aphrodisiacs!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「道理でまったく知らないと思った……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No wonder I didn’t know anything about it...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えー、でも本当に効果あるんだよー？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh, but it really works, you know?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ちーっともそんな気なかった女性もとろとろ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even women who didn’t have any such feelings become drowsy."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　作り方も簡単でこんな風にー……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It’s easy to make, like this—...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だーっ、作るな作るな！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Nooo, don’t make it, don’t!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「出来ちゃった……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It got made...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「出来ちゃいましたね……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It’s been made...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　強力な胃薬……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A powerful stomach medicine...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「に、媚薬効果も混ぜたものー♪」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And it also has aphrodisiac effects mixed in♪\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「これ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"This...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　一応胃薬として効くことは効くんだよね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Should work as a stomach medicine at least.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そのはずですよ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It should...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「媚薬効果はともかく……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Putting the aphrodisiac effect aside...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　胃薬としては効果があるかどうか、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "whether it really works as a stomach medicine,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ちゃんと確認しないと……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "we have to properly check...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「の、飲むんですか！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-you’re going to drink it!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「自分で作ったもの、自分で飲まずに、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If you don’t drink what you make yourself,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　人に飲ませるわけにはいかないだろう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "you can't make others drink it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それに、作ったものを捨てるってのも……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Also, throwing away what you made is..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あはは、晩ご飯の残り物処分する",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Haha, like how a mother disposes of leftover dinner"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お母さんみたいだね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "stuff.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「黙ってな！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Shut up!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「媚薬効果なんて、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Aphrodisiac effects,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　別に死ぬわけじゃあるまいし、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it’s not like it’ll kill me or anything,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　こんなもん大したことないよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so it’s not a big deal.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あっ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "言うが早いか、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Before she could finish saying that,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "プリマは媚薬効果つき胃薬をひょいパク。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Prima quickly popped the aphrodisiac-effect stomach medicine into her mouth."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「プリマさん？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Prima-san?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「――さっきまでキリキリしていた",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"—the sharp stomach pain I had just now"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　胃の痛みがすーっと消えた」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "has completely disappeared.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うふふん。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ufufun."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私だって薬師のはしくれだもーん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I’m also an apprentice pharmacist, after all.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……なーんか納得いかない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Somehow, I’m not convinced.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、あの、体の変化はそれ以外は？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"U-um, are there any other changes to your body?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "プリマは自分の顔を覆って、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Prima covered her face,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "黙ってしまった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and fell silent."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、あのぉ〜？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"U-um~?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　プリマさん？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Prima-san?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うわ、すごい……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Wow, incredible...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「すごいんですか！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Is it really that incredible!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「完っっ全に……予想以上だった……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Com-pletely... beyond expectations...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「天才エロ薬師、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The genius erotic pharmacist,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ミル・ヨークスのお手製だもーん。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Mil Yorks’ own handiwork, after all."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そりゃガツンと効くものじゃないとねー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It has to hit hard, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほーら、体がー、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"See, your body—"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どんどん熱くなってくるでしょ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "is getting hotter and hotter, isn’t it?\""
    }
  ]
}

